    "description": "Nankai Tatsumura Construction Co., Ltd. engages in the construction and real estate businesses in Japan. The company is involved in contracting and design of civil engineering, architecture, plumbing, electrical and telecommunications construction and works, and other general construction works. It also offers renovation work and large-scale repair work for condominiums, as well as net zero energy house services. In addition, the company engages in the structural and architectural design and construction management; and maintenance and management of railway facilities, including track construction, electrical construction, and signal and communication construction. Further, it undertakes road construction, river construction, water supply and sewerage facility construction, and residential land development work. The company was founded in 1923 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan. Nankai Tatsumura Construction Co., Ltd. is a subsidiary of Nankai Electric Railway Co., Ltd."
